  RFC7664 [label="RFC7664
Dragonfly Key Exchange
2015", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC7664.html", target="_top", tooltip="This document specifies a key exchange using discrete logarithm cryptography that is authenticated using a password or passphrase.  It is resistant to active attack, passive attack, and offline dictionary attack.  This document is a product of the Crypto Forum Research Group (CFRG)."];
